  "text": "To our knowledge, there is little, if any, consensus recommendation about the management of paediatric patients with CD, particularly with regard to the risk of tumours, although different supervision protocols are established for patients >18 years [CITATION_1] [CITATION_2] [20] [CITATION_3] .",
